The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Roshan to be back in India
                                                   Roshan to be back in India
            A STAFF REPORTER                      
	Calcutta: Roshan Mahanama has been named as the Match Referee for the three-Test series between hosts India and South Africa. According to an ICC release on Thursday, Asad Rauf and Tony Hill will be in charge of the Chennai Test.         
	In WEST INDIES         
	 Match Referee: Chris Broad         
	 March 22-26  WI vs SL (Test), Guyana: Simon Taufel and Billy Bowden         
	 April 3-7  WI vs SL (Test), Trinidad: Simon Taufel and Billy Bowden         
	 April 10  WI vs SL (ODI), Trinidad: Simon Taufel and local appointment         
	 April 12  WI vs SL (ODI), Trinidad: Simon Taufel and local appointment         
	 April 16  WI vs SL (ODI), St Lucia: Simon Taufel and local appointment         
	In INDIA         
	 Match Referee: Roshan Mahanama         
	 March 26-30  Ind vs SA (Test), Chennai  Asad Rauf and Tony Hill         
	 April 3-7  Ind vs SA (Test), Ahmedabad  Billy Doctrove and Tony Hill         
	 April 11-15  Ind vs SL (Test), Kanpur  Asad Rauf and Billy Doctrove                                                                                                                       
